content: Really quick, while its fresh, what do you think wrong with LinkedIn post? I understand there is risk in everything and that no one knows how things are going to act in the wild, but where do you think we went wrong or I didn't do something I should have that you were telling me to do? I feel like we did enough things to have this go very differently. What do you think went wrong, an honest assessment of me on this. Don't hold any punches.
